description: This awesome taco man is handing out the tastiest tacos with handmade tortillas, fresh salsas, and highest-quality meats you may find out on the LA streets. Whether you’re homeward bound and need to make a quick pit stop to chow down on these savory, authentic creations, or want to please your guests at your next event with this fantastic food & service, El Chingon Taco Co. is the perfect choice for you.
name: El Chingon Taco Co
